{"tid":2319118,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"送車師「撐我捱落去」","createTime":"2020-12-10T01:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T08:19:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"822bf5a831aa2416cbe64cb9eaffe0da82d34d13","tid":2319118,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T01:12:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/TW33YJIN6FETFI23L7RLT4PXT4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FTW33YJIN6FETFI23L7RLT4PXT4%2F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpvch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=7fa0c224\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FTW33YJIN6FETFI23L7RLT4PXT4%2F&h=6bcba9a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/TW33YJIN6FETFI23L7RLT4PXT4/</a><br />\n<br />\n送車師「撐我捱落去」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/q3bAPi-DPGkEPK1f-2_pF7dUuu0=/1000x707/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E34EZOBYJFHCPBHSALWEYV22VE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fq3bAPi-DPGkEPK1f-2_pF7dUuu0%3D%2F1000x707%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE34EZOBYJFHCPBHSALWEYV22VE.jpg&h=a32a2181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方在庭外警告及提醒等候囚車的人群或違反限聚令。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】在囚室內過着不知時間流逝的日子，周庭最期待收信和探訪時光，並對「送車師」那股幹勁大為感動，<span class=\"orange\">「知道外面有人支持自己，先會有力量捱落去」</span>。惟警方昨在囚車出入口架設大批鐵欄，禁止任何人接近囚車，就連拍打車窗「送手足」的權利也失去。只能遠望囚車駛離的七旬翁「總之點樣我都支持佢」，寄語周庭在獄中好好照顧自己。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：6.21圍警總案  官：上訴勝算低 周庭被拒保釋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警禁靠近囚車 阻記者拍攝<br />\n<br />\n周庭的facebook小編日前出貼，透露周庭在判刑當日，<span class=\"orange\">看見送車師追趕並高舉紙牌，感動到靠在身旁婆婆身上哭泣</span>，貼文中日文並用，更讓日本傳媒認識送車師。昨散庭後，大批支持者在囚車處守候，但警方不斷播放錄音，提醒在場人士違反限聚令等規例會被票控，並要求所有記者掛上記者證。當囚車駛出前，警方更拉起橙帶封鎖法院外的半條金鐘道，禁止支持者靠近囚車，又一度阻礙記者拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n在人群當中，73歲的李先生尤其顯眼，他因未趕及入庭旁聽，只好守候囚車離開。他透露多年來一直支持周庭，「佢哋係睇清楚香港嘅情況，喺我心目中，佢哋係被迫出嚟爭返個主權」，見證一國兩制的崩壞。他嘆息道：「𠵱家完全係一國一制，只係官員唔同，但官員諗法同共產黨一樣。」他寄語周庭在獄中好好照護自己，「總之點樣我都支持佢，總之佢係唔會令我失望嘅一個人」。<br />\n<br />\n在袋上掛着「煲底相見」的陳小姐昨趁休假，特意前來旁聽，她稱讚三子具備政治智慧之餘亦相當勇敢，指從片段中看見他們無畏無懼地包圍警總，亦禁不住落淚。陳坦言，周庭保釋被拒雖是預料之內，但聞判一刻仍難掩失落。談到向三子的寄語，她哽咽道：「我哋喺出面、有自由嘅香港人會堅持落去，希望佢哋撐住。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JLPcOAx17k6nDTzu_CAeNbCKEl8=/591x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EQBVXQHZUFDW7N6DFFBDX6HBKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJLPcOAx17k6nDTzu_CAeNbCKEl8%3D%2F591x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEQBVXQHZUFDW7N6DFFBDX6HBKE.jpg&h=110edeee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳小姐稱讚三子具備政治智慧之餘亦相當勇敢。<br />\n<br />\n============<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"373e6e8b12e6c26200012529f2280e30484ffbbb","tid":2319118,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T01:19:29.000Z","msg":"香港變左臭港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑白癲倒"},{"pid":"40bbf6bbb60811fc9b8caa2180fb2bf1c6d8faaa","tid":2319118,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T01:23:51.000Z","msg":"周庭最期待收信和探訪時光，並對「送車師」那股幹勁大為感動，「知道外面有人支持自己，先會有力量捱落去」<br />\n<br />\n透露周庭在判刑當日，看見送車師追趕並高舉紙牌，感動到靠在身旁婆婆身上哭泣，貼文中日文並用，更讓日本傳媒認識送車師。<br />\n<